Rating: 3
Good flavor and a very simple recipe. There is too much cornstarch in the recipe, I needed to add more milk and cook the pastry cream a little longer than directed to get rid of the cornstarch taste.

Rating: 2
I have made this twice, and believe this is too much cornstarch to use. Thickened way too much,tasted "cornstarchy", had to add half and half to save it! Next time I will cut cornstarch in half and see.

