Rating: 4
Very easy to prepare. Perfect color and texture. Sweet, great for a lge fruit tart or many mini tarts. Made first batch with vanilla bean; second batch without. You'll notice a BIG difference in perfume and aroma of the cream as it cooks-use the vanilla if you can.